values:
ok so friday night i went to don pablos with kristina which was real fun! wooo lol we go there too much haha but we love it..so i came home did some stuff then went to bed for the state cup staurday. so everyone met at the perry hall bowling alley in that little shopping center and we carpooled with deanna! woo! lol we ate a lot of pretzels lol and i sang very lovely..heh and talked and laughed a lot, but i forget about what lol but it was fun..so we get there an hour before the game so we practiced for an hour lol then deanna, jess, and i got into the triangle and started passing and a guy with these all red shoes walked by and jess was like i like your shoes!! lol so he was like thanks... and once he left jess like did that little gag thing haha god jess! if you dont have something nice to say, dont say it at all! lol so then out of no where shes like omg he looks like a clown! so deanna and i start cracking up haha cuz his shoes were like gold !! haha and he had like red wavy hair lol soo funny and the game before went into overtime and then into pks so we sat through that too which was fun to watch cuz you could see that the other team had better skill and all and the one team's goalie didnt even try to get the ball rolling on the ground into the corner..it was kinda pathetic cuz i mean she couldve at least tried! well anyway we started and holy crap these girls have skilll lol the CSA hornets i think it was..but i mean they were division 1 wags so we played really good but mr terry says we could be like division 3 or something so they won. it wasnt bad though. we played really good. mr terry said if we play this hard in the league we'll definetely win all our games. cuz we lost our last two games and havent been playing as hard..the score was 4-1..the one goal linds was in goal and they made a shot but it was on the ground.. not really fast or ne thing. and linds goes to pick it up and it rolls right through her hands. i felt soo bad for her.. but it was kinda funny.. heh..lol but it was really fun..they had this skilled player sammy and she got carded!! haha but just yellow cuz she was pushing a lot with amanda then she got all mad and yelled at manda and the ref and it was amusing..i wanted to hit her though lol but our goal was soo awesome lol cuz sam's awesome at soccer like that lol its true..but yeah you can look at d's lj to see it if you want..
so then we went to leave and we were hungry so of course our parents get lost haha fun times! so then we happen to be right on my dad's house road!! lol that was awesome lol that road is called prefferkorn or something like that haha and im like thats his house!!!! haha im such a loser lol so we finally got home and went to silver spring..yum yum!! and deanna saw some lady teacher so she talked to her and then our little blinky buzzer thing went off and it wasnt vibrating yet so i thought deanna broke it lol but she didnt..so then that guy got deanna and i shirley temples..yumm but i mean who cares who gets more cherries right?! lol and i wouldnt try that food haha im sucha wimp lol so then all of a sudden deanna's like awww! and our parents like both turn around lol and d starts cracking up lol it was soo funny..they looked like twins!! haha and deanna's mom and my mom were funny and my mom said shes never been so entertained at dinner..haha so then deanna asked if i wanted to spend the night and i said well duhhh lol not really but i did say yes lol so i went home and got a shower and came over..lol we got online then ate some apple pie yummm lol and watched she gets what she wants haha i love that bonjour yall heh it makes me laugh lol but the movie was kinda corny excpet the little boy was amusing. so then we had to take natalie out and we kept hearing something and natalie wouldnt do her business!!! haha funny funny so we were just standing there and talking for a while lol like we need to see a scary movie with the guys omg thatd be so much fun! lol so then we went to bed oh and we attacked each other with highlighters lol fun fun haha and then deanna started whispering so i was like wth?! lol and i was freaking out cuz the room kept getting dark then light then dark then light lol so deanna told me to shut my eyes haha so we got up and i ate cinnamon life..holy frick that stuffs good! lol so i got more and deanna was gonna pour milk in my cereal cuz i didnt want any that time so i was like NO! haha so then i was like whoa i sounded like a ninja! lol good times so then we got dressed and went to the mall where deannas mom got me a shirt thank youu!! it matches deanna! woohoo hehe so deanna was looking at the purses and shes like its (how ever much money) mom..and shes like deanna, you dont wear purses..so deanna like gives her this look and says so i cant start wearing them ever in my life?! haha it was funny lol so the oc shirt wasnt too boxy lol so we got it..yay!!! haha so we left and were in the car and deanna wanted to see the keychains and my keys and i have this thing you pull out and its if someone or a animal is following you or chasing you and it makes a loud noise to scare them away so deanna was like how do i pull it out?! so im like you pull the whole thing out! haha and it was soo loud in the car lol jesus!! haha deanna started laughing so hard and said it was fun haha loser jkk lol good times..i love you deanna! so many good times to come!! 
so then i went to my grandparents and that was normal..fun i guess

lunch--wow fun again!
wc--i forget what was soo funny but it was funn

l/a--haha so much fun again! mr strazz sprayed me with the water haha and omg em lol my eraser! we laughed for soo long! haha soo many good times in our group haha it hit me on the cheek haha then you did it to everyone lol that was soo funny!

well gotta get ready for softball and eat..

omg this week was so great! i was really woo and finally talked to eamon lol its an improvement..i might start sitting with d and them on certain days and darc on the other but i dont know..ok well i dont feel like going through everyday, lets see i was mainly thinking about a guy every minute and had it going great until today and someone said something, dont know who but i just need to straighten things out one time or another. uh soccer was really fun..deanna and i get drunk i swear, lol we laughed the whole time. it was hilarious we'd make fun of mr terry in the good way of course lol and we'd start cracking up in drills haha love you deanna! and omg spanish was sooo much fun today! everyone was making animal noises so senora made us shut the doors and was like on the count of tres, everyone make their best animal sound as loud as they can lol omg soo funny we laughed forever and ben got sprayed with water haha and senora imitating jahi lol wow i love my spanish class soo much! the dance was the thing that got me upset but i turned out fine like always lol umm d and i cant dance! haha rach..lol im not entirely bad haha then show me a move if your so good! noooo lol so many good times..and holy crap 8 six graders like eamon..so i was like i swear if he goes out with one of them, ill never talk to him again lol why cant he just like someone?! godddd lol sorry im done..omg cant wait for tomorrow though! state cupp babbyyy!!! woo carpooling with doreo..haha we're gonna get so drunk lol but im nervous too..heh

well update whenever..

k lets see where i left off..softball practice wednesday night was funn..i had to pitch and i was ok but i lost it in the end..lets see i got a homerun and ran a homerun off of ashley's hit cuz she hurt herself..hope it gets better ashley!! and alli who also hurt herself lol im gonna get hurt next lol good times..haha singing sidewalks to ashley and alli petted toby woby boo boo lol abbey

math-we did that walky thing and none of the girls were raising their hand, so mr j goes michelle! i saw your hand go up! and im like uhhh no it didnt! and hes like well then you were definitely stretching so im like no but fine..so i go up and i dont know what i was doing or if i did good but they clapped for me so i was like woo! so then i got a sticker at the end of class and he said thanks for being cooperative lol woo fun fun

then came home and headed to the blast game baby! lol joanna omg it was soo much fun..we didnt play long but we won 4-1 against MHR soccer i think it was..i scored twice! woo and janet and joanna scored..is that perfect or what?! and everytime you hit the wall it shocked you lol the sub box, haha we all touched it and went owwwwwww!!! lol soo much fun! then we sat down and i had a slice of pizza from mr dennis thank you!! then went to walk around the stadium and we met the coach of the team we played..he was cool but seemed a little woo kinda like me heh but he was friendly then we had these little 7-8 year olds next to us and they were soo cute!! hehe but they would like run from our whole team if we got near them lol fun fun..then went back and watched the game...they lost in a painful overtime where the ball went right through the goalies legs..thats ok though but #17 scored twice too! lol whoop whoop haha..so much fun! singing all the songs..haha that looks like oprah! thats john..oh lol sorry john! it was far away..and i sing songs randomly like someone else heh and john tried to get a candy bar hah that worked..and aw john did joannas hair well tried to do it in a braid lol it was so cute lol i love you guys!

then today i had practice for soccer..wooo it was funnnn dunno why it just was..i love my soccer team..we're so awesome..lol you know it lol anyway i got a new soccer ball juggling record! 19!!! woot woot lol fun fun then my mom got some more sizes for the sweatshirts! woo and the ladder haha good job kelsey! lol jk and lol sam was like out of it..haha sam? sam? uhh sammmmm..? lol huh? lol good times!


then came home and talked to some people-nothing too great...

then called joanna cuz kris and caitlin and kris'school friends were going to the movies and she and janet went with me! woo so much fun guys! it was all normal..omg we saw sahara..it was soo good and scary! lol we were all like holding each others hands lol we're soo pathetic haha and janet cut off my circulation haha omg im soo scared!! me too, me too!! lol we screamed at the doll hah we started cracking up at stuff and that lady looked at us lol fun fun and the sour patch kids too lol thanks caitlin! they were yummmyyyyy lol so we finshed the movie and my mom picked us up and we started talking about the new curfew(sp?) thats starting at the avenue and how dillon walker, barteck, and buddy were on the news about it the other night..so my mom was like well how do they know your not sixteen? you could be really short, and its not like everyone has an ID lol funny so we all had problems haha so we'd start spazzing if a security guard came up to us lol omg soo funny! we can start barking lol janet chases her tail lol then we can make fake IDs lol where? kinkos! haha that was soo random lol love you guys soo much!


and now im here..i love you abbey no matter what, ok? your friends are here for you all the time!

lets see monday..i dont really remember at all lol except eamon saw darc and i looking at him finally lol it was funny not that you care lol so anyway softball was funnn!! hehe good times alli and ashley..ch ch ch ch chelsea! alalbabal lol alli i couldnt do you haha i learned the alligator..woo i want ashelys seat in science too lol im so pathetic..

gym omg so much fun..we got to queen court and that was fun and omg rach is soo funny lol wow i love you girls..so then we were leaving and all my keychains on my purse were gone lol so i was like freaking and made char and rachel late cuz they were waiting for me lol thanks guys! but i got to my locker and they were in my bookbag lol sorry you two! haha fun fun times

going to softball and not soccer..but i will miss soccer and deannas going to softball!! haha i love you deanna but i said your going to softball so you are! lol

woo today was an awesome day or shall i say half day! haha im so funny..not lol
omg this morning was an awesome morning for me..lol but you dont have to understand cuz i know deanna does lol woo i was soo happy!! we were cool this morning with all the guys..hah lol and then swids started saying something to me like michelle, now that we are "friends" i think its right that you know deanna....and then i missed the rest cuz ben we being too loud lol but whatever sorry deanna lol and we started talking about busch gardens and it was funny lol..ok so it was really weird going to spanish first but sooo much fun! i forget what was soo funny but i remember senora was like what are you doing tonight? and jahi's like how do i say 5 hours with mr fishler after school!!! and then he starts making fun of him then omg adam pulls his pants up REALLY high and it was soo funny cuz he was walking around like that lol i love my spanish class! they're awesome lol 
then l/a we had the lock down but watched taming of the shrew in mute mode and compared it to taming of the shrew with sound..it was pretty fun cuz ms shanks showed us some pictures of conner too and then had to turn the tv back on and it was really loud so mr. s and her were like freaking out cuz we were still in the lock down lol it was funny..
then world cultures was all research..easy stuff today..fun fun
then lunch..it was good and funny. ms shanks came over and was like how do you guys like the student teacher? so rachel's like michelle thinks hes hot! and i was like yeah i know..and ms shanks was like well i figured lol funny and then rachel started talking to levy wevy omg lol it was funny though
then gym..it was funnnn..rachel was the team captain of our team but i was the one who was actaully cheering everyone on! i was awesome lol but it was me, rachel, charlotte, brooke, rachel f, and some girl lol but we won 2 games and we beat ashley/steph/shannon/tiffany/laura/paige/ashleys team!! woo lol sorry guys but we needed to beat you cuz sometimes it seems like you think you guys are the best..pfft we're good too...lol jk you guys were fun to play!!

well going to this open house thingy with deanna and kristina(maybe) and her mom..we might do something before but i dont know..woo it shall be interesting! lol well update later or whenever..

i dont remember much of yesterday..it was good though..my mom forgot to give me a lunch so i was begging for food from people lol jk but steph did give me a dollar and i only asked joanna but got some food from rach and dar war lol thanks guys..
omg then soccer..dum dum dum..i swear it was torture!!! 2 of the whole perry hall high "backyards"!!! omg it was soo tiring but i was proud of myself and deanna lol oh and jess!! lol..i showed up with my socks and chin-guards on so i took them off and had to roll my socks down so i had the awesome socks!! lol wooo everyone was like drunk lol the headballs..shelby was so hilarious lol but good! and then we had 2 more pointless drills which were more running and touch and pass drills..boring but the scrimmage was funn thank you rachel!! lol she put deanna and i on the same team!! woo cuz that like never happens..and i was being an idiot and like i forgot deanna was going to camp with me even though i asked her where she wanted to go lol its that 5 second memory thing again lol good times..
then my dad took me to friendlys yummm and we saw rachel outside..i got a burger and then ordered my reeses pieces sundae but couldnt finish it lol 

so yeah then came todayy and had another awesome day!!!
science was actually fun!! omg it was a record!! lol and darc and i were actually together in a lab!! lol she counted off weird too..then mathh!!! yessssss joanna lol we beat domonkos and steph!! wooooo lol so much funnn..we wanted to dance and scream lol we both got 100's on the math test which means i probably have a b now with the extra credit in there too(thanks shannon) !!! woo im soo happy lol sorry..ill stop now..then world music we took a break from everything and watched this gay movie and kasey and i were dying through the whole thing so we started to read my math book lol fun times!! then cooking, ms hartmen did the demonstrations for the bambinos and cori and i were like omg we're not eating that thing and then we tried it and we're like "omg this is good!!!" lol it was funny then lunch was good and fun. world cultures was easy and stuff..just research the l/a was fun i participated lol wooo and we brought up the song "your so vain" and i like loved it when i was younger so i was like i know that song!!! lol then spanish was soo funny like usually with our jokes and tatoos haha senora and hookers lol adams nuts lol dont ask..so many good times there and the cool chiwawauu(lol sp?) game woo!

going to dinner with kristina at damons soon..woo even more fun!

if someone can do something tomorrow say something..

wooo i spent a little over 24 hours with my lovely deanna! hehe lol
k so her mom dropped her off and we were trying to make my little water thing work and it wouldnt so my mom came to help and we had to keep filling it up and my mom pressed this button and this hyena(sp?)noise went off and deanna's face was funny lol soo we got online and i asked her if she wanted bowling or movies so we decided the movies and picked ice princess at 7:05 heh and so my mom was being mean to deanna lol not really but it was funny..so my mom said do you wanna eat before or after the movie said we said before..so like we stayed on the computer for a while and finally my mom tells us we need to go somewhere soon so i asked deanna what she liked and she said tacos so i thought taco bell!
